<section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 249, 249); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3月7-8日，为庆祝“三八”妇女节的到来，经济管理学院27期学班入党积极分子陪伴培养人度过了一个愉快而又难忘的节日，他们为女性培养人送上了自己精心准备的礼物，营造了一个温馨、和谐、团结、奋进的工作氛围。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEIT8yIichn2d35xBHRWcnEzfuP3IGsVqvhOeKZXX2Cw4xDqAw8f5ne2KG9AG9FOj5xRicZHXLxKSBlQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="293" height="201" style="width: 293px; height: 201px;"/></p></section><p><section style="margin: -25px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(135, 70, 70); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; pad